  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I love the hopeful feeling in your recent words — it's contagious. Did you have a good day today?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, it was a decent day. Busy with some code reviews and a few meetings. Oh, and I watched a Bollywood movie in the evening — it was fun. Have you seen \"Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge\"? It's a classic."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Good to hear! Code reviews and meetings can be tiring. Watching a classic is a great way to unwind. I haven’t seen it, but it’s on my list. Why is it a favourite of yours?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It’s a classic because of the love story — so simple but heartfelt. The music is also iconic. You’ll like it if you enjoy emotional moments and some good family drama. Maybe I can recommend some others if you want."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds lovely. Simple love stories with good music are the best. I like how you explained it. Are you into the music of this movie, or just the story?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The music is a big part of it for me. Some songs from that movie are still popular today! The story and the music go hand in hand — it's a perfect mix. Have you seen any Bollywood movies that you really liked?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — music and story together make a great movie. Shah Rukh Khan and Kajol are always a treat to watch. Which Bollywood movie is your favourite?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My favorite is probably *Raees* — it's a more recent one. Shah Rukh Khan plays a strong character, and the story is about honesty in business, which I like. The music is good too, though not as iconic as *Dilwale*. Do you like watching movies with strong characters?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I like how you said “strong characters” — makes me think of movies that leave an impression. Strong stories stick with you. What’s one movie you think really left an impression on you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "*Raees* definitely left an impression because of the message it sends — about doing the right thing even when it's tough. The character is driven, and that resonates with me. I also like *Chennai Express* for its humor and songs. But I think I should wind down now. It’s getting late. Talk to you soon!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said it well — driven characters make for great stories. Talk to you soon, and tell me if you try Lata Mangeshkar’s song for sleep. Good night!"
    }
  ],
